在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">爆炸性的社交媒体长篇小说中，坎耶后来声称“统治”对他的妻子</a>：“我对妻子有统治。这并不是不像女权主义者那样醒来的。她和一位亿万富翁在一起，为什么她会听你们中的任何一个愚蠢的屁股打破母狗？</p><p> “人们说红地毯的外观是她的决定……是的，我不让她什么都不想做，但是如果我的认可，她绝对无法做到，你愚蠢的屁股醒了。透明</p><p>在韦斯特（West）的推文之后，有报道称这对夫妇正在前往离婚，但是， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rep-denies-rumours-that-kanye-west-and-bianca-censori-are-reportedly-getting-a-divorce-3837866">这对说唱歌手的代表米洛·扬诺普洛斯（Milo Yiannopoulos）否认了这一点</a>。</p><p>现在，韦斯特声称，唱片学院没有给他任何参加活动的门票，他必须为获得红地毯而战。</p><p>说唱歌手于2月15日（2月15日）上周六（2月15日）上X/Twitter，当他的歌曲“嘉年华”获得最佳说唱歌曲的提名时，他应该被邀请。 </p><figure id="attachment_3833940" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833940" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833940" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3833940" class="wp-caption-text"> Kanye West和Bianca Censori在2025年格莱美奖上。图片来源：Robyn Beck/AFP通过Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “格莱姆斯怎么能提名我，然后不给我门票，然后当我离开时人们生气。我不得不战斗5个小时，并打电话给我认识的每个人，才能获得格莱姆的门票。他们最终给了我门票，但仅用于红地毯。那时我还没有开始<a href="https://www.complex.com/music/a/markelibert/ye-criticizes-recording-academy-tickets-grammy-red-carpet" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>横冲直撞</em></a>。”</p><p>他所指的“横冲直撞”是他随后的格莱美派推文，这使他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">对犹太社区的道歉撤销了他过去的反犹太言论</a>，然后继续宣布自己为“纳粹”，并写道：“我爱希特勒”（Love Hitler），以及赞美亿万富翁和X老板<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/elon-musk">埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）</a> ，是“在Twitter上曾经在Twitter上亮着的人”，这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/elon-musk-sparks-backlash-with-nazi-like-gesture-at-trump-inauguration-3830625">后者在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统就职典礼上的纳粹主义指控</a>之后。</p><p>进一步的帖子使他嘲笑其他边缘化社区，声称“奴隶制是一种选择”等。然后，他擦拭了自己的网站，开始只出售<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-releases-new-song-beauty-and-the-beast-before-stripping-yeezy-site-to-only-sell-swastika-t-shirt-3836729">一件白色T恤，胸口上有一个大刀柄</a>，被列为“ HH-01”  - 可能是对“ Heil Hitler” Chant的引用。 </p><figure id="attachment_3837737" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837737" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837737" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWest-copy.jpg" alt="坎耶·韦斯特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWest-copy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWest-copy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWest-copy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWest-copy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWest-copy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWest-copy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837737" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特。图片来源：Jeff Kravitz/Filmmagic/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>狂欢看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-x-account-has-been-deactivated-after-bizarre-weekend-rant-3836418">他的X帐户被取消并停用</a>，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-shut-down-kanye-wests-yeezy-website-for-selling-swastika-t-shirt-matthew-koma-responds-with-fuck-ye-merch-3837155">Shopify然后关闭了West的Yeezy网站</a>。后来确认说唱歌手已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-dropped-by-talent-agency-following-anti-semitic-posts-3837245">被他的人才机构放弃，</a>他的前任参谋长退出了Yeezy公司。</p><p>除了他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-returns-to-twitter-x-after-ban-and-deletes-racist-posts-3837746">X页再次变得活跃</a>外，周四还看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-says-kanye-wests-site-was-removed-over-fraud-potential-not-swastika-t-shirt-3837621">Shopify指出，由于欺诈的可能性，该艺术家的网站被删除了 - 不是因为它正在出售Swastika T恤</a>。</p><p>自从社交媒体上咆哮以来，你们的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kanye-west-ty-dolla-sign-vultures-1-review-lyrics-tracklist-3585917">“秃鹰”</a>合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ty-dolla-ign-condemns-hate-speech-following-kanye-wests-anti-semitic-posts-and-swastika-t-shirt-controversy-3837549">ty dolla $ ign谴责了他的仇恨言论</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charlie-puth-begs-kanye-west-to-stop-promoting-incredibly-dangerous-messages-and-swastika-tee-3837062">查理·普特（Charlie Puthe）恳求韦斯特（Charlie Putgg）停止推广“令人难以置信的危险”信息，</a>而<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/friends"><em>朋友的</em></a>明星大卫·施温默<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/david-schwimmer-calls-for-action-against-kanye-west-after-nazi-comments-silence-is-complicity-3836363">（David Schwimmer）则要求采取行动采取行动。说唱歌手</a>是他充满仇恨的“纳粹”帖子的说法，认为“沉默是同谋”。</p><p>在其他地方，Ye曾被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-sued-for-discrimination-and-accused-of-texting-hail-hitler-to-jewish-yeezy-employee-3837691">一名前Yeezy雇员裁定，并被指控向犹太工作人员发短信给“ Hail Hitler”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-claims-he-and-bianca-censori-were-only-given-tickets-to-grammys-red-carpet-3838596">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）的后声称，他和比安卡·辛森（Bianca Censori）仅获得了格莱美奖红地毯的门票，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
