om">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Selena-Gomez-and-Benny-Blanco.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_GG2025_Penske-Media-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Selena-Gomez-and-Benny-Blanco.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_GG2025_Penske-Media-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Selena-Gomez-and-Benny-Blanco.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_GG2025_Penske-Media-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Selena-Gomez-and-Benny-Blanco.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_GG2025_Penske-Media-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Selena-Gomez-and-Benny-Blanco.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_GG2025_Penske-Media-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Selena-Gomez-and-Benny-Blanco.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_GG2025_Penske-Media-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Selena-Gomez-and-Benny-Blanco.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_GG2025_Penske-Media-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/benny-blanco">本尼·布兰科（Benny Blanco）</a>用一个装满纳乔奶酪的浴缸为他的未婚夫赛琳娜<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/selena-gomez">·戈麦斯（Selena Gomez）</a>感到惊讶。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/emilia-perez-review-zoe-saldana-selena-gomez-flawed-musical-melodrama-3805570">“ Emilia Perez”评论：ZoeSaldaña和Selena Gomez放开了有缺陷的音乐情节剧</a></strong></li></ul><p>制片人于2月14日（2月14日）上Instagram展示了大手势。在视频中，他展示了通往他浴室的玉米饼芯片的踪迹，在地板上有更多的“我[爱]你”。</p><p>在剪辑中，标题为：“当你的未婚夫不是一个鲜花的女孩时，”布兰科继续展示装满融化奶酪的浴缸，里面蘸上碎屑，然后咬一口。</p><p> “我喜欢这一切。”戈麦斯在评论中写道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https: